      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project! This vehicle is looking for a dedicated owner who can give it the major mechanical and cosmetic attention it needs to get back on the road. It\u2019s a fantastic opportunity for a DIY enthusiast or someone looking for a valuable parts car at a budget-friendly price!",
