      "id": "sybil_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, preserved with fastidious attention to detail. Every surface reflects a commitment to excellence, offering the discerning driver a rare opportunity to acquire a machine that transcends the standard pre-owned market. Experience uncompromising performance and aesthetic perfection in a vehicle that presents as if it just departed the assembly line.",
